	- similar neuron datasets (auxiliaryNeuronsAutoFeatureDatase) are still created during train phase.
	- auxiliary neurons and their output connections are still trained during train phase.
	- however if(auxiliaryNeuronsAutoInference): auxiliary neuron input connections are dynamically trained during each inference step (and then immediately disgarded): 
